display_long_description:
Become a real CSI agent today and learn how you can solve realistic CSI cases on your own. You will be guided step-by-step by your personal lab assistant, as you solve the mysteries.
Labster is designed to let you discover the wonders of science through hands-on virtual practices in a realistic and immersive laboratory environment. You will have your own fully equipped laboratory where you can perform experiments as scientists do in real-life.
Our labs are based in real research performed in top universities, and you will learn cutting edge techniques utilized right now by researchers around the world.
Labster gives you immediate feedback and continually tests your learning throughout the experience.


Please note that this app is currently a demo version only, but we still highly encourage and appreciate feedback. As the app is only a demo version we are unable to provide support if you experience issues
